refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;
public Imagick Imagick::channelFxImage stringexpression
Applies a mathematical channel expression to the image, allowing channels to be extracted, exchanged, or combined, and returns the result as a new image.

&reftitle.parameters;


  expression

   A channel expression describing how the source channels are combined and copied, for example "red; green; blue".
